data.description:
This Georgetown gem has everything you've been dreaming of! With 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half baths, and a spacious 2-car garage, it's both luxurious and practical. The attic space above the garage offers potential for storage or expansion. Inside, the updated flooring and carpeting create a cozy yet elegant atmosphere. The refinished stairs and ship lap details add charm and character throughout.
But the real showstopper? The in-ground saltwater pool and jacuzzi, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests in your exceptional yard. And for those cooler evenings, the beautiful 3-season room with heat ensures you can enjoy the space year-round. Plus, with brand new vinyl luxury planks, this home is not only stylish but also low-maintenance. Don't let this opportunity slip awayif Georgetown where you've always wanted to live, this home is a must-see!
